|ager <tt>(astute)</tt>
|agil (it.<''agile'', fr.<''agile'')<br><tt>(agile)</tt>
|-
|aqua <tt>(water)</tt>
|ap<U+0103> <tt>(water)</tt>
|acvatic (it. <''acquatico'', fr.<''aquatique'') <br><tt>(aquatic)</tt>
