|ce, ci
||{{IPA|/t<U+0283>/}}
| ''ch'' in '''chest''', '''cheek'''
| ''cerc'' (circle), ''cine'' (who)
|-
|che, chi
||{{IPA|/k/}}
| ''k'' in '''kettle''', '''kiss'''
| ''chem'' (I call), ''chimie'' (chemistry)
|-
|ge, gi
